    {
      "id": "el_10",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 100,
      "width": 397,
      "height": 15,
      "text": "Weighted Avg & Combined Groups",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 10,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Weighted Avg & Combined Groups",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_11",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 125,
      "width": 398,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "Weighted Avg = Σwᵢxᵢ / Σwᵢ\n\nCombined Avg of two groups:\n  = (n₁×A₁ + n₂×A₂) / (n₁ + n₂)\n\nAlligation: n₁/n₂ = (A₂-Avg)/(Avg-A₁)\n\nWHY: Larger groups pull average towards them.\nWeighted avg gives more influence to larger groups.\n\nEx: 3 items avg 10, 2 items avg 20\n  = (3×10+2×20)/(3+2) = 70/5 = 14",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 11,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Weighted Avg = Σwᵢxᵢ / Σwᵢ\n\nCombined Avg of two groups:\n  = (n₁×A₁ + n₂×A₂) / (n₁ + n₂)\n\nAlligation: n₁/n₂ = (A₂-Avg)/(Avg-A₁)\n\nWHY: Larger groups pull average towards them.\nWeighted avg gives more influence to larger groups.\n\nEx: 3 items avg 10, 2 items avg 20\n  = (3×10+2×20)/(3+2) = 70/5 = 14",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
