    {
      "id": "el_17",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 434,
      "width": 351,
      "height": 219,
      "text": "Same distance: Avg = 2ab/(a+b)\n  (Harmonic Mean — always < simple avg)\n\nSame time: Avg = (a+b)/2\n  (Arithmetic Mean = simple average)\n\nGeneral: Total Distance / Total Time\nNEVER just average the speeds!\n\nWHY: Same distance → more time at slow speed,\nso avg is pulled towards the slower speed.\n\nEx: 60 km at 30 km/h, 60 km at 60 km/h\n  Avg = 2×30×60/90 = 3600/90 = 40 (NOT 45!)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1700,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 17,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Same distance: Avg = 2ab/(a+b)\n  (Harmonic Mean — always < simple avg)\n\nSame time: Avg = (a+b)/2\n  (Arithmetic Mean = simple average)\n\nGeneral: Total Distance / Total Time\nNEVER just average the speeds!\n\nWHY: Same distance → more time at slow speed,\nso avg is pulled towards the slower speed.\n\nEx: 60 km at 30 km/h, 60 km at 60 km/h\n  Avg = 2×30×60/90 = 3600/90 = 40 (NOT 45!)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
