    {
      "id": "el_26",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 797,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Sum = 12+15+18+21+24 = 90\nStep 2: Avg = 90/5 = 18\n\n  |──12──15──18──21──24──|\n               ↑ Avg=18\n\nTRICK:\nAP series → Avg = (First+Last)/2\n= (12+24)/2 = 18 (middle term!)\n\nAnswer: Avg = 18 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
