      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Count = 50-11+1 = 40 numbers\nStep 2: Sum = (11+50)x40/2 = 1220\nStep 3: Avg = 1220/40 = 30.5\n\nTRICK:\nAny AP: Avg = (First+Last)/2\n= (11+50)/2 = 30.5\nWorks for any consecutive/AP series!\n\nAnswer: Avg = 30.5 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
