    {
      "id": "el_41",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1211,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Natural 1..50: sum=1275, avg=25.5\nStep 2: Even 2..60: sum=930, avg=31\nStep 3: Odd 1..79: sum=1600, avg=40\n\nTRICK:\nNatural(n) → (n+1)/2 = 51/2 = 25.5\nEven(n) → n+1 = 31\nOdd(n) → n = 40\nDon't confuse with nth term!\n\nAnswer: 25.5, 31, 40 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4100,
