      "groupIds": [
        "type_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Natural 1..50: sum=1275, avg=25.5\nStep 2: Even 2..60: sum=930, avg=31\nStep 3: Odd 1..79: sum=1600, avg=40\n\nTRICK:\nNatural(n) → (n+1)/2 = 51/2 = 25.5\nEven(n) → n+1 = 31\nOdd(n) → n = 40\nDon't confuse with nth term!\n\nAnswer: 25.5, 31, 40 ✓",
