    {
      "id": "el_46",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1227,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 159,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Old sum = 10x15 = 150\nStep 2: New sum = 11x16 = 176\nStep 3: New student = 176-150 = 26\n\nTRICK:\nNew = NewAvg + n x (NewAvg-OldAvg)\n= 16 + 10x(16-15) = 16+10 = 26\n(n = original count)\n\nAnswer: Age = 26 years ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
