      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Old sum = 10x15 = 150\nStep 2: New sum = 11x16 = 176\nStep 3: New student = 176-150 = 26\n\nTRICK:\nNew = NewAvg + n x (NewAvg-OldAvg)\n= 16 + 10x(16-15) = 16+10 = 26\n(n = original count)\n\nAnswer: Age = 26 years ✓",
