      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1146,
      "width": 415,
      "height": 33,
      "text": "The average weight of 8 persons is 65 kg. One person\nweighing 80 kg leaves. What is the new average weight?",
      "fontSize": 13,
