      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Old sum = 8x65 = 520\nStep 2: New sum = 520-80 = 440\nStep 3: New avg = 440/7 = 62.86 kg\n\nTRICK:\nDrop from avg = (80-65)/7 = 15/7\nNew avg = 65 - 15/7 = 62.86\n(removed person was above avg)\n\nAnswer: New Avg = 62.86 kg ✓",
