      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1487,
      "width": 415,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "A person travels from A to B, a distance of 120 km, at 40\nkm/h and returns at 60 km/h. What is the average speed for\nthe entire journey?",
      "fontSize": 13,
