      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1885,
      "width": 415,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "A batsman has an average of 40 runs in 10 innings. How\nmany runs must he score in the 11th inning to raise his\naverage to 45?",
      "fontSize": 13,
