    {
      "id": "el_86",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2350,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Each +5: new sum = 900+100=1000\n  Avg = 1000/20 = 50\nStep 2: Each x3: new sum = 900x3=2700\n  Avg = 2700/20 = 135\n\nTRICK:\n+x → Avg+x=50  |  xk → Avgxk=135\nTRAP: if only 3 of 20 numbers +10\nAvg up by 3x10/20 = 1.5 (NOT 10!)\n\nAnswer: +5 → 50, x3 → 135 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
