    {
      "id": "el_91",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 2318,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Sum=45, n=9 → Mean=5\nStep 2: Sorted: 1,2,3,4,5,7,7,7,9\n  Median = 5th value = 5\nStep 3: Mode = 7 (appears 3 times)\n\n  1,2,3,4,[5],7,7,7,9\n           ↑ Median\n\nTRICK:\nMean=sum/n, Median=middle value\nMode=most frequent\nMode ~ 3xMedian - 2xMean\n\nAnswer: Mean=5, Median=5, Mode=7 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 9100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 91,
