      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_14"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Sum=45, n=9 → Mean=5\nStep 2: Sorted: 1,2,3,4,5,7,7,7,9\n  Median = 5th value = 5\nStep 3: Mode = 7 (appears 3 times)\n\n  1,2,3,4,[5],7,7,7,9\n           ↑ Median\n\nTRICK:\nMean=sum/n, Median=middle value\nMode=most frequent\nMode ~ 3xMedian - 2xMean\n\nAnswer: Mean=5, Median=5, Mode=7 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
